{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And again, that-- the middle of the night, we heard in Hungarian, first, anybody has jewelry, money, silverware has to get rid of what.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "If anybody is caught with it is going to be shot forthwith.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And about 15 minutes later we heard the same story-- anybody with jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "But this time, it wasn't spoken in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "This time it was spoken in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And the Germans took over in Kosice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "They took over the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "I don't know every train or every second-- I mean every box or every second car, there was like a little [NON-ENGLISH], like a little [NON-ENGLISH] where the soldier was standing up, you know, in the train.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "He was standing up where he could have a view.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Every few cars had like a soldier was there, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And that's all you heard in the train, going, go, go, go, go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Even today, whenever I travel a train, you know-- pop, pop, pop-- that's the first thing that comes back to my mind is-- is-- is-- is the-- is the railroad.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "It was going until the next day around the afternoon we reached the place that must have been Slovakia, Slovakia, because I pulled myself up and I saw people which were not Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And the fields were beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "This was in May, late May.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Countryside was gorgeous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the elderly people in the car would say, which way are we going?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somebody said, we are heading north.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then someone says, if we are heading north, we're in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we are heading towards Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want you to know that we were in Hungary until 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We still didn't know what the Holocaust-- the Holocaust was going full blast in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Millions of Jews were killed in Russia, the Ukraine, France, all the occupied countries.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hungary was the last country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My village, the Russians were in my village that October.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only six months prior to that, the Russians already were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the last action of the Germans during World War II.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They lost the war already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the biggest atrocities took place when they killed the Hungarian Jews in a matter of-- in a matter of six, seven weeks-- they killed close to half a million Jews in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway, in Kosice-- in Slovakia, they opened the door and we had a chance to empty out the buckets, and to fill in some new water.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] they locked the doors again, and we started to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And again, all day, all night was going-- going until a day later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the first day [NON-ENGLISH]-- 1944.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first day [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like 2 o'clock in the afternoon, and the train pulled in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I seen people when I looked through the little bit window I seen people dressed in stripe-- in stripe uniforms.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they opened up the doors and everybody said, [GERMAN], everybody get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told us to leave all the bundles on the-- on the-- on the-- what do you call it by the train there?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Platform.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the platform.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said, what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're going to get the bundles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now everybody got busy starting to write their names and addresses on the bundles, because if we are going to come back to pick up the bundles, we wanted to know which is our bundle.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody got busy with pens, with crayons, they started to write, to write, you know, the name, the address.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was busy writing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, you know, there were soldiers with dogs and they said, out, everybody, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they announced that all men, like from age 15 to 40, 45, I don't remember exactly, to stand on one side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then all women a certain age, and all children and mothers with children should keep on going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I stood with my brother, because my brother, Mordcha, he was with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as-- as-- as my column was moving along, I saw my mother with my other sister and brother-- and brothers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was like a little teary eyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was like crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know if she sensed something-- but really, I don't think anybody knew what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my brother motioned to me that I should send Mordcha over to her, my little brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My brother maybe was a year, two years younger than me-- Mordcha.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she motioned to me that I should send over Mordcha to her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I told Mordcha to go to be with my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so they all-- we all went one side.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
